name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Salesforce - Load All Objects And Fields

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Load all objects and fields in salesforce objects manager

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple chrome extension that makes all Objects in the object manager,
and all object fields load at once, instead of lazy loading as one scrolls
✅ Enables searching with the browser using Control/command+F
✅ This extension is completely open source and does not collect any user data.
